[\fB-t\fP \fItype\fP] [\fB-P\fP PIDfile][\fB-d\fP] [\fB-e\fP] [\fB-a\fP] [\fB-o\fP] [\fB-i\fP \fIaddress\fP] [\fItcp:port\fP] \fIdev\fP 
